    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/3aca2172eca97dfa5afffcc552042eb4.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/3aca2172eca97dfa5afffcc552042eb4.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=242 height=37 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/ac0dca56ee67005a4ba59f55258541c3.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" width=610 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/ac0dca56ee67005a4ba59f55258541c3.webm?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/d43566dfd493832fa54ab9eebeb7edf8.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/d43566dfd493832fa54ab9eebeb7edf8.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=186 height=37 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/c6f48463fed4589e6a1fd875a9ff065f.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" width=610 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/c6f48463fed4589e6a1fd875a9ff065f.webm?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/da549a026c0ea46000a666bf73c81652.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/da549a026c0ea46000a666bf73c81652.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=37 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/11f900cde0c39f99172fa37c9342e6d7.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" width=610 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/11f900cde0c39f99172fa37c9342e6d7.webm?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re Mikan, a no-nonsense cat running a struggling shelter with your human companion, Matsue. Rescue strays, match them with adopters, and keep the lights on without losing your morals. Every decision counts. Do you turn away a sick cat when you're low on funds? Or approve an adoption that doesn’t feel quite right?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/cb96a12316f0434780977486bca90676.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/cb96a12316f0434780977486bca90676.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=339 height=36 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/f147a8c9ed2b7fe69fe6850b79ec528c.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" width=610 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/f147a8c9ed2b7fe69fe6850b79ec528c.webm?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/b9ca92688248b26e35411b12a4878e2a.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span> <strong>Rescue and Rehabilitate:</strong> Each cat has its own unique personality. Some quickly warm up; others require patience and special attention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/b9ca92688248b26e35411b12a4878e2a.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span><strong> Find the Perfect Match:</strong> Carefully evaluate potential adopters. A mismatched adoption might ease finances but risks a cat's happiness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/b9ca92688248b26e35411b12a4878e2a.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span> <strong>Customize Your Shelter:</strong> Expand and upgrade your shelter, designing spaces and even opening a cat café to attract visitors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/b26110ce46e3d81d2542a2f672bfb01b.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/b26110ce46e3d81d2542a2f672bfb01b.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=36 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/8733a8d9559b9ecd5d6a531487d88e1b.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span><strong> Moral Dilemmas with Real Stakes</strong> – Every decision impacts the shelter’s future. Should you prioritize financial stability over waiting for the perfect adopter?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/8733a8d9559b9ecd5d6a531487d88e1b.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span><strong> Playful Cat Battles </strong>– Inspired by classic fighting games, combat is anything but typical. Use <strong>real cat behaviors</strong> like ignoring foes for emotional damage, kicking litter, scratching, and even sitting on enemies’ faces. Players execute on-screen key combos to attack, heal, or defend in a battle system unlike anything seen in standard RPGs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/8733a8d9559b9ecd5d6a531487d88e1b.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span><strong>A Cat’s Perspective on Communication</strong> – Matsue can only hear &quot;meow.&quot; You might be telling her to buy food, but she thinks you need the litter box cleaned. Misinterpretations affect how the shelter runs, leading to unexpected (and sometimes hilarious) outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/8733a8d9559b9ecd5d6a531487d88e1b.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span> <strong>Real-World Impact – Support Shelters While You Play</strong> – Through <strong>limited-time in-game charity bundles</strong>, a portion of proceeds will go to real-life cat rescues. Players can unlock exclusive in-game rewards, such as cat outfits, shelter decorations, and special-themed items, while helping real cats in need.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/a13bd4ad4a851afba35d9d83ad8c048f.apng?t=1766350508\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/a13bd4ad4a851afba35d9d83ad8c048f.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" class=\"bb_img\" width=663 height=36 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/0b412abc19644564a1506c32099406b7.webp?t=1766350508\" width=22 height=19 /></span> Immerse yourself in a charming world blending pixel art and soft, painterly visuals. Experience warmth, humour, and depth in each moment spent at the shelter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One cat can change everything. Will you help Mikan transform Neko House into a prosperous sanctuary?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/633c3c641d40d567755853ad79c55c93.poster.avif?t=1766350508\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/633c3c641d40d567755853ad79c55c93.webm?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317250/extras/633c3c641d40d567755853ad79c55c93.mp4?t=1766350508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
